      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahdus Jaunektus/ pee\nka ne kahdas Wainas buhtu/\nvēt statsns un saprattigus/\neckſch wiſchdas Gudribas/ un\ntas Atſitſchanu ſinnatu/ un kam\ngudrs Prahtsbuhtu/ un kas der-\nrigi buhtu Kehnina Pilli ſtab-\nweht/ ka tee taptu painahziti\neckſch to Kaldeeru Gramatahm\nun Wallopaß."
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Kehninsch ſpreede\nteen/ kas ikdeenas teem bij ja-\ndohd/ no ta Kehnina Barribas/\nun no ta Wihna/ ko wiſch dseh-\nre/ un ka tee trihs Gaddus ta\ntaptu audſinati/ un ka tee pehz\nta Kehnina Preckſcha ſtahwetu."
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Starp teem nu bija no\nJuha Behrneem/ Danijs/\nAnanijus/ Misaëls un Asarijs."
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to Kambar-Junkuru\nUṣraugs dewe teen zittus Wahr-\nDus/ un noſauze Danijelu Bel-\njazer/ un Ananiju Sadraf/ un\nMisaëlu Mesek/ un Asariju A-\nbednego."
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Danijs apschinahs\njawā Sirḍi/ ka tas ne gribbohts\nfagahuitees ar ta Kehnina Bar-\nribas nedā ar ta Wihna/ ko\nwiſch dsehre/ tadeht luhdfe\nwiſch to Kambar-Junkuro Uṣ-\nraugu/ ka tam Waika buhtu ne\nfagahuitees."
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews dewe Danije-\nlam Schehlastibu un Apschehlo-\nchanu preckſch to Kambar-Jun-\nkuru Uṣrauga."
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Kambar-Ju-\nru Uṣraugs fazzija us Da-\nlu: Es bihstohe mannu Ka-\nto Kehnina/ kas juhta Ehi-\nun Dsehreenu ta irr nospre-\nkapehz bij winnam redseht/\njuhsu Waigi leefakt buhtu/\nto zittu Jaunektu/ kas\nlihdsitr/ tad weddiſeet juhe-\nmannu Galivu to gattapu\nwi pee ta Kehnina."
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Danijs fazzi\nMelzaru/ ko tas Kambar-\nkuru Uṣraugs bij eezehlis\nDanijsu/ Ananiju/ Misaë-\nAsariju."
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Baudi jelle ar ta\nKalpeem kahdas deſmits\nnas/ un dohd mums Ba-\nno Semmes Angteem ebs-\nUhdeni dsert."
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tad lai luhto\nmuhfu Gihmis buhs\nPreckſcha/ un to Jaunektu-\nnis/ kas ta Kehnina Ba-\nehō/ un darri tad ar ta\nKalpeem ka tu patā redseti"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad paklaufija\nteen ſchinni Leeta/ un be-\nar teem deſmits Deenas."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz deſmits\nnahm tappe redsehts/ ka\nGihmis ſtaistaks/ un\nMeeſas jo taukas bija/\nwiſtu zittu Jaunektu/ kas\nKehnina Barribas ehde."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atnehme M-\nwinnu nospreestu Barri-\nto Wihnu/ ko teem bij dse"
    }
  ],
